://blogs.wsj.com/briefly/2016/08/04/5-things-to-know-about-thailands-proposed-constitution/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2016年，巴育通过拒绝提名[[泰国僧王|泰国僧王]]来延期{{le|僧伽最高委员会|Sangha Supreme Council}}的决定，<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.nationmultimedia.com/news/national/aec/30290322|title=Prayut refuses to submit nomination of Somdet Chuang as Supreme Patriarch|work=The Nation|accessdate=2017-09-12|language=en|archive-date=2018-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181118150631/http://www.nationmultimedia.com/news/national/aec/30290322|dead-url=no}}</ref>直到一条规定泰国政府可绕开僧伽最高委员会而直接任命泰国僧王的法律出现。<ref name="Nation 2016">{{Cite news|url=http://www.nationmultimedia.com/news/breakingnews/30303081|title=NLA passes Sangha Act amendment bill|date=2016-12-29|work=The Nation|accessdate=2016-12-31|via=|archive-date=2016-12-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230152743/http://www.nationmultimedia.com/news/breakingnews/30303081|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bangkokpost.com/news/general/1194416/somdet-phra-maha-muniwong-new-supreme-patriarch|title=Somdet Phra Maha Muniwong new Supreme Patriarch|work=Bangkok Post|accessdate=2017-02-09}}</ref>

在2017年，巴育通过44号协议用[[特别调查局_(泰国)|泰国特别调查局（DSI）]]官员取代了{{le|国家佛教机关|National Office of Buddhism}}。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://in.reuters.com/article/thailand-buddhism-idINKBN1640EX|title=Thai junta replaces director of Buddhism department with policeman|agency=Reuters|accessdate=2017-03-24|archive-date=2018-02-04|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6wzPqSGw7?url=https://in.reuters.com/article/thailand-buddhism/thai-junta-replaces-director-of-buddhism-department-with-policeman-idINKBN1640EX|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而，在2017年8月，该官员因被抗议为污损僧侣形象的改革而被巴育调职。Phra Buddha Issara认为军政府轻易就在压力面前退缩。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://in.reuters.com/article/thailand-buddhism-idINKCN1B91EP?rpc=401&|title=Thailand's Buddhism chief removed after pressure from religious groups|last1=Tanakasempipat|first1=Patpicha|date=2017-08-29|accessdate=2017-08-29|agency=[[路透社|路透社]]|last2=Niyomyat|first2=Aukkarapon|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112022801/https://in.reuters.com/article/thailand-buddhism-idINKCN1B91EP?rpc=401&|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年5月，在镇压完政变周年日的抗议活动之后，全国维持和平与秩序委员会同时在四个寺庙中采用雷达系统以逮捕数名僧侣。<ref name=":32">{{Cite news|url=http://www.khaosodenglish.com/news/crimecourtscalamity/calamity/2018/05/25/buddha-issara-followers-fume-at-defrocked-monks-arrest/|title=Buddha Issara Followers Fume at Defrocked Monk’s Arrest|date=2018-05-25|work=Khaosod English|accessdate=2018-05-26|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180525120637/http://www.khaosodenglish.com/news/crimecourtscalamity/calamity/2018/05/25/buddha-issara-followers-fume-at-defrocked-monks-arrest/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.smh.com.au/world/asia/thailand-raids-temples-arrest-monks-in-fight-to-clean-up-buddhism-20180525-p4zhhv.html|title=Thailand raids temples, arrest monks in fight to clean up Buddhism|last=Wongcha-um|first=by Panu|date=2018-05-25|website=The Sydney Morning Herald|language=en|accessdate=2018-05-26|archive-date=2018-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180525120456/https://www.smh.com.au/world/asia/thailand-raids-temples-arrest-monks-in-fight-to-clean-up-buddhism-20180525-p4zhhv.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>令官员们感到惊讶的是，被捕的其中一名僧侣就是Phra Buddha Issara。这位右翼立场的僧侣被指控多条罪名，如2014年的所谓抢劫和耽搁官员，但最为严重的指控还是2017年的非法使用皇家印章。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.khaosodenglish.com/politics/2018/05/24/buddha-issara-arrested-in-dawn-raid/|title=Buddha Issara Arrested in Dawn Raid|date=2018-05-24|work=Khaosod English|accessdate=2018-05-25|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180524110205/http://www.khaosodenglish.com/politics/2018/05/24/buddha-issara-arrested-in-dawn-raid/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-thailand-buddhism/thailand-arrests-senior-monks-in-temple-raids-to-clean-up-buddhism-idUSKCN1IP0X3|title=Thailand arrests senior monks in temple raids to clean up Buddhism|agency=Reuters|accessdate=2018-05-25|date=2018-05-24|archive-date=2018-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180524120052/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-thailand-buddhism/thailand-arrests-senior-monks-in-temple-raids-to-clean-up-buddhism-idUSKCN1IP0X3|dead-url=no}}</ref>警方并没有解释为何因一些早在4年前的指控将他逮捕，一位活动家表示他相信这是来自一位神秘人物的命令。促使全国维持和平与秩序委员会加紧对佛教控制的前参议员Paiboon同样表达了他对此事件的惊讶。<ref name=":3">{{Cite news|url=http://www.khaosodenglish.com/news/crimecourtscalamity/calamity/2018/05/25/buddha-issara-followers-fume-at-defrocked-monks-arrest/|title=Buddha Issara Followers Fume at Defrocked Monk's Arrest|date=2018-05-25|work=Khaosod English|accessdate=2018-05-26|language=en-US|archive-date=2018-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180525120637/http://www.khaosodenglish.com/news/crimecourtscalamity/calamity/2018/05/25/buddha-issara-followers-fume-at-defrocked-monks-arrest/|dead-url=no}}</ref>所有被捕的僧侣都被立刻解除僧职，且在未被审判的情况下被非法扣留。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bangkokpost.com/news/crime/1472209/senior-monks-defrocked-after-raids|title=Senior monks defrocked after raids|date=|work=Bangkok Post|accessdate=2018-05-26}}</ref>

=== 二度当选总理 ===
2018年10月28日，在[[2017年泰國憲法|2017年泰國憲法]]下，首相是由{{le|泰国参议院|Senate of Thailand}}需由{{le|全国维持和平秩序委员会|National Council for Peace and Order}}指名并和[[泰國眾議院|泰國眾議院]]一道选出<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bangkokpost.com/news/politics/1565758/young-voters-find-voice|title=Young voters find voice|last1=Jotikasthira|first1=Om|last2=Sabpaitoon|first2=Patpon|work=Bangkok Post|date=2018-10-28|accessdate=2019-01-10}}</ref>。 政党可以提名任何人代表他们党参选，包括无党籍人士。许多人认为巴育计划从亲军部政党[[人民國家力量黨|人民國家力量黨]]的250名参议员与国会议员中得到选票。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bangkokpost.com/news/politics/1546578/pm-allows-ministers-to-back-parties|title=PM allows ministers to back parties|last1=Sattaburuth|first1=Aekarach|last2=Bangprapa|first2=Mongkok|work=Bangkok Post|date=2018-09-26|accessdate=2019-01-10}}</ref>

2018年11月1日，{{link-th|泰国副总理列表|รายชื่อรองนายกรัฐมนตรีไทย|泰国副总理}}{{tsl|en|Somkid Jatusripitak||Somkid Jatusripitak}}在一场[[福布斯|福布斯]]会议上表示他认为下任首相会和巴育相似<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bangkokpost.com/news/politics/1568014/face-of-next-pm-will-be-similar-to-prayut|title=Face of next PM will 'be similar to Prayut'|last=Arunmas|first=Phusadee|work=Bangkok Post|date=2018-11-01|accessdate=2019-01-10}}</ref>。

2018年11月28日，巴育表达过他想要在大选後继续担任[[泰国首相|首相]]职位。由于他并不属于任何政党，舆论认为巴育会借助{{le|泰国宪法|Constitution of Thailand|新宪法}}中做修改的点来让自己连任<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.nationmultimedia.com/detail/opinion/30359420|title=Election has already been won, so what now?|website=The Nation|date=2018-11-28|format=Opinion|accessdate=2019-01-10|archive-date=2019-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190324024430/http://www.nationmultimedia.com/detail/opinion/30359420|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2019年1月下旬，巴育内阁的4位成员辞职投入[[人民國家力量黨|人民國家力量黨]]工作。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.bangkokpost.com/news/politics/1619878/palang-pracharath-ministers-resign-from-cabinet|title=Palang Pracharath ministers resign from cabinet|last=Limited|first=Bangkok Post Public Company|accessdate=2019-01-30}}</ref> 之後，[[人民國家力量黨|人民國家力量黨]]宣布了该党的首相提名候選人人中包括巴育。

2019年6月5日，巴育所控制的[[人民國家力量黨|人民國家力量黨]]在[[2019年泰國眾議院選舉|眾議院選舉]]中获得115席，成为第二大党。通过与小党合作在泰国国会两院共同举行的首相指名选举中获得500票，被选为泰国首相<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://jp.reuters.com/article/thailand-politics-idJPKCN1T62PJ|script-title=ja:タイ、プラユット氏を首相に選出 親軍政の連立政権発足へ|newspaper=Reuter Japan|agency=Thomson Reuter|date=2019-06-06|accessdate=2019-06-06|archive-date=2021-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314121357/https://jp.reuters.com/article/thailand-politics-idJPKCN1T62PJ|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

