*在与海外泰裔群体谈话时，巴育说：“...很多群体尝试将我们的君主与其他国家的君主相比。这是无法做到的，因为我们的君主制有着长远的历史。我们的君主就像是神灵。我们的君主与其他任何实体无关。他逾越于一切争议之上。当他被侮辱时，我们需要动用类似于诽谤罪的刑法第112条，因为当我们被侮辱时，我们可以提告，但如果是国王被侮辱，王室无法控告对方。这是因为我们国王与其他任何实体无关，他在宪法之下，在政府为保护他而建的法之下。可人们将这视为人权问题。试问：若有人侮辱你父亲，你会退缩吗？我们不会。但在这种情况之下，他们能够控告。而国王因与他物无关，他无法控告，谁将维护他？泰国国民要承担此重任。任何不懂得这道理的人都不是泰国人民。这些人很糟糕。这是敏感话题。我想要让观众来解释泰国国王与他国君主的不同。”<ref>{{cite news|title=Junta Chairman Lectures Youth on Thai-style Monarchy & Democracy [Transcript]|url=http://www.khaosodenglish.com/detail.php?newsid=1436349932|accessdate=2015-07-09|work=Khaosod English|date=2015-07-08|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304085836/http://www.khaosodenglish.com/detail.php?newsid=1436349932|archivedate=2016-03-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==個人生活==
巴育的[[乳名|小名]]是「ㄉㄨ◌̌」（{{Lang-th|ตู่}}；{{RTGS|''Tu''}}）<ref>{{cite news|title=Top Adviser to HM King Showers Praises on Junta|url=http://www.khaosodenglish.com/detail.php?newsid=1440569441&typecate=06&section=|access-date=28 August 2015|work=[[Khaosod_English|Khaosod English]]|date=26 August 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304192420/http://www.khaosodenglish.com/detail.php?newsid=1440569441&typecate=06&section=|archive-date=4 March 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref>，在媒體通常稱他「ㄉㄨ◌̌叔叔」（{{Lang-th|ลุงตู่}}；{{RTGS|''Lung Tu''}}），他的反對者通常欺負稱呼「ㄉㄨㄅ◌̌」（{{Lang-th|ลุงตูบ}}；字意：小狗）。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.matichonweekly.com/scoop/article_69570|title=ใครเริ่มเรียก 'ลุงตู่' คนแรก ? ดังข้ามปี ชื่อนี้ที่มา ไม่ธรรมดา !!|author=ปรัชญา นงนุช|date=10 December 2017|publisher=มติชนสุดสัปดาห์|access-date=25 May 2019|archive-date=2021-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211215100750/https://www.matichonweekly.com/scoop/article_69570}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=打開原因，為何人家需要懂皇家的寶藏：透淺新聞 (เปิดสาเหตุ! ทำไมประชาชน ต้องสนใจกับสมบัติของเจ้า กันหนักหนา: เจาะข่าวตื้น 263); at 19:13|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=49oxzyo32Cc|via=YouTube|access-date=7 July 2021|archive-date=2021-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211215100755/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=49oxzyo32Cc}}</ref>巴育的妻子{{link-en|娜拉邦·占奥差|Naraporn Chan-o-cha}}曾經為朱拉隆功大学语言学院前副教授。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.bangkokpost.com/thailand/politics/428293/general-gets-ready-to-swap-into-civvies |title=General gets ready to swap into civvies |last=Nanuam |first=Wassana |date=23 August 2014 |work=[[Bangkok_Post|Bangkok Post]] |access-date=4 September 2014 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20211017120309/https://www.bangkokpost.com/thailand/politics/428293/general-gets-ready-to-swap-into-civvies |archive-date=2021-10-17 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref name=PrayuthFamily>{{cite news|title=First family keeps low profile|url=https://www.nationthailand.com/politics/30241498|access-date=22 November 2014|work=[[The_Nation_(Thailand)|The Nation]]|date=22 August 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211017121455/https://www.nationthailand.com/politics/30241498|archive-date=29 August 2016|url-status=live}}</ref>娜拉邦在 2010 年被选为陆军参谋长起。她在媒体采访承認說要丈夫在媒體要更冷靜一點，此外，她也說要所有丈夫隱私家事如衣服、化妆和剪髮都是她的責任，又說巴育喜歡「英格蘭風格」。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Chachavalpongpun|first1=Pavin|title=Prayuth's Wife Called Thailand's 'Most Able'|url=https://www.asiasentinel.com/p/ablest-woman-thailand-naraporn-chan-ocha|access-date=27 June 2015|work=[[Asia_Sentinel|Asia Sentinel]]|date=5 January 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025225057/https://www.asiasentinel.com/p/ablest-woman-thailand-naraporn-chan-ocha|archive-date=25 October 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>他們有雙胞胎女兒。<ref name=Haworth />

巴育公开表示他頻繁咨询算命先生 Warin Buawiratlert，算命家说寻求建议没有坏处。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Thongnoi|first1=Jitsiree|title=Prayut, the fortune teller and the ghost of the guru|url=https://www.bangkokpost.com/thailand/special-reports/690736/prayut-the-fortune-teller-and-the-ghost-of-the-guru|access-date=13 September 2015|work=[[Bangkok_Post|Bangkok Post]]|date=13 September 2015|archive-url=https://archive.today/20211017114914/https://www.bangkokpost.com/thailand/special-reports/690736/prayut-the-fortune-teller-and-the-ghost-of-the-guru|archive-date=2021-10-17|url-status=live}}</ref>在他担任首相初期发烧和疼痛时，他将自己的病痛归咎于政敌施放的咒语，并用圣水与疾病作斗争。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Satrusayang|first1=Cod|title=Addicted to superstition: Thailand's 21st century mystics|url=https://www.bangkokpost.com/thailand/general/457038/addicted-to-superstition-thailand-21st-century-mystics|access-date=16 January 2015|work=[[Bangkok_Post|Bangkok Post]]|date=15 January 2015|archive-url=https://archive.today/20211017114835/https://www.bangkokpost.com/thailand/general/457038/addicted-to-superstition-thailand-21st-century-mystics|archive-date=2021-10-17|url-status=live}}</ref>据[[曼谷郵報|曼谷郵報]]报道，巴育有一套幸运戒指，每一種活動都循環使用，他还要喜歡戴了一个象毛手镯来避厄运。<ref name=Fernquest>{{cite news|last=Fernquest|first=Jon|title=PM Prayuth's lucky rings|url=http://www.bangkokpost.com/print/432936/|website=Bangkok Post|access-date=31 March 2015|date=18 September 2014}}</ref>他鼓勵人家穿{{link-en|皇家正式風格服|Formal Thai national costume}}。<ref name=Fernquest />

在[[2019冠状病毒病泰国疫情|COVID-19]]大流行期间，巴育因在2021年4月的COVID-19疫苗接种会议上未戴口罩而被罚款6,000泰铢。<ref>{{cite news |last=Sivasomboon |first=Busaba |url=https://apnews.com/article/health-thailand-bangkok-coronavirus-business-b9f89c920164494ac50a1f008198b895 |title=Thailand's prime minister fined for breaking face mask rule |work=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |date=26 April 2021 |access-date=20 May 2021 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512005354/https://apnews.com/article/health-thailand-bangkok-coronavirus-business-b9f89c920164494ac50a1f008198b895 |archive-date=12 May 2021 |url-status=live}}</ref>作为总理，巴育每月的薪水为 75,900 泰铢，外加每月 50,000 泰铢的职位津贴，他没有担任国防部长的薪水。<ref>{{cite news |title=Curfew in Greater Bangkok from Monday |url=https://www.bangkokpost.com/thailand/general/2146271/curfew-in-greater-bangkok-from-monday |access-date=9 July 2021 |work=[[Bangkok_Post|Bangkok Post]] |date=9 July 2021}}</ref>

他的母語是[[首都泰語|首都泰語]]，在[[2019年泰國眾議院選舉|2019年政治運動]]，巴育在泰國東北部，但很害羞講東北泰語，而所有的活動卻講自己的方言。<ref>{{cite web|title='大肚' 撒嬌求孔敬-呵叻公民選舉 有甜蜜說「愛東北泰國，為了自己的東北泰國，願意死掉」('บิ๊กตู่' อ้อนขอคะแนนโคราช-ขอนแก่น หวานใส่ "ฮักหลายเด้อ ยอมตายเพื่ออีสานบ้านฉัน"); at 19:13|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vYgs9DF1YVY|via=YouTube|access-date=5 March 2022|archive-date=2022-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220305091955/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vYgs9DF1YVY}}</ref>

